        "text_EMQtwr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sustainability: “The quality of causing little or no damage to the environment and therefore able to continue for a long time.”</p><p>- Cambridge Dictionary</p><p>To us at Arms of Andes, environmental sustainability in fashion industry means <strong>not harming the environment in all stages of production including the garment's end of life...</strong></p><p>So, what stages in fashion can cause harm to the environment?</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "color": "#4a4a4a",
